not easy (ROOT is quite big, CLHEP has almost unusable cmake build
files). You fight packaging for ROOT here [1] and for CLHEP here [2].
ROOT works, CLHEP not really.

[1] https://salsa.debian.org/science-team/root
[2] https://salsa.debian.org/science-team/clhep

